ns0:DescribedValueSet.ns0:Purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set contains concepts that represent patients who have had an office or other outpatient visit for preventive care.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use the Quality Data Model (QDM) datatype related to Encounter, Performed.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes only relevant concepts associated with comprehensive history, evaluation, and management of a patient in an office or outpatient facility. Patient can be presenting with problems that are minor to high severity. This is an extensional value set of CPT codes.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes non-office visits, including telehealth services.)
